metadata.name: AIWRLDS Membership Pass
metadata.description: What is AI WRLDS ? AI WRLDS is a membership program granted to holders of an AI PUDGY. Holderâ€™s of an AI WRLDS membership card will be granted free claims for a lifetime to collections created by the AI WRLDS team and that they collaborate with. Future collections brought to the AI WRLD ecosystem will be voted on by the community using the WRLD DAO. We will be working to bring other membership card programs with less perks for non AI Pudgy holders.
